videos.description: Maryland's Bruno Fernando shows off his shooting skills by hitting an and-1 jumper while being double-teamed by Buckeyes' defenders.
videos.headline: Fernando nails and-1 jumper while being double-teamed

videos.description: Darryl Morsell comes away with a steal and finishes the fastbreak with a 2-handed slam.
videos.headline: Morsell flushes jam off Buckeyes' fastbreak

videos.description: Anthony Cowan Jr. pulls up from deep to extend Maryland's lead.
videos.headline: Cowan shows off his range

videos.description: Bruno Fernando comes away with a chase down block on an Ohio State fastbreak.
videos.headline: Fernando hustles back on defense for an emphatic block

videos.description: Maryland's Anthony Cowan Jr. knocks in a deep 3 at the shot clock buzzer to seal the win vs. Ohio State.
videos.headline: Cowan hits from near the half-court logo
